---
Source:
  - Title: Bone of Space
    ISBN: 978-0942795066
By: Seung Sahn
Page: 5
---
Quiet night
Sitting silently in the mountain cabin

    in complete stillness.
Moonlight dills all space.

Why does wind from the West
Shake the forest?

        A bird shrieks.
The sound slowly fades
As it flies through the cold sky.
